# ba3bf07668994c8a91014f1ee500e900
#: ../../admin-guide/plugins/generator.en.rst:23
msgid ""
"The `Generator` allows testing of synthetic workloads by generating HTTP "
"responses of various sizes. The size and cacheability of the response is "
"specified by the first two coomponents of the requested URL path. This "
"plugin only supports the ``GET`` and ``HEAD`` HTTP methods."
msgstr ""

