#: ../../admin-guide/plugins/generator.en.rst:32
msgid ""
"``cache`` or ``nocache``. If ``cache`` is specifed, the `Generator` "
"plugin will respond with ``Cache-Control`` headers marking the response "
"as cacheable for 24 hours. Integral number of bytes to return in the "
"response."
